{"tid":2260124,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大興行動基地疑傳出刺鼻氣體惹示威 事隔一年再多四人被控今提堂","createTime":"2020-10-27T10:43:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T12:34:12.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c89da6186491d324953989298fde3fcf217b1a12","tid":2260124,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T10:43:42.000Z","msg":"去年10月有網民質疑警方於屯門大興行動基地進行催淚彈測試，導致刺鼻氣體四處蔓延，過百名市民前往基地抗議，其間發生警民衝突。事隔一年，再有四名男女被控非法集結等罪，當中包括去年屯門區議會選舉候選人張贊華。案件今於屯門裁判法院提堂，辯方要求押後案件，以便索取法律意見。案件押後至12月22日再訊，被告獲准以2,000元現金保釋，其間須每周向警署報到。<br />\n<br />\n早前已有26人被控提堂，相關案件將轉介區域法院審理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201027/RF6DNZVSGRDS3BH6BXZWNUESAU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201027%2FRF6DNZVSGRDS3BH6BXZWNUESAU%2F&d=BCqMRPjRs%2BrlYbPtDS4RDIm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=0f0129ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201027%2FRF6DNZVSGRDS3BH6BXZWNUESAU%2F&h=cd177051\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201027/RF6DNZVSGRDS3BH6BXZWNUESAU/</a>"},{"pid":"e300e834122e730a9dc680106f2f6a1777c6951f","tid":2260124,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T10:45:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"848d4212d250bdb84795014ae58a3facc7e3485b","tid":2260124,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T10:46:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2819d8de409c2db43b0b833806a62d86697bd5f","tid":2260124,"uid":231480,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T10:47:01.000